00:10:48.250 --> 00:10:54.070
List out their characteristics, purposes
and differences, and then find the option

00:10:54.190 --> 00:10:56.440
that correctly points out the distinction.

00:10:57.050 --> 00:10:59.150
Shortcuts and smart techniques.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:04.010
