00:11:24.230 --> 00:11:27.709
This seriously increases your
chances of getting it right.

00:11:28.219 --> 00:11:32.689
Have some contextual understanding
for policy impact questions.

00:11:32.900 --> 00:11:35.180
Think about the bigger economic picture.

00:11:35.569 --> 00:11:39.620
If inflation is high, you know
the central bank will likely do

00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.420
something to reduce the money supply.

00:11:42.055 --> 00:11:44.695
Also try to memorize acronyms.

00:11:45.085 --> 00:11:50.755
Knowing the full forms and basic
